# AI Office - Agency Operations Directory

This directory contains operational files for the AI Office virtual agency.

## Structure

```
office/
├── clients/           # Client profiles and communications
│   └── <client-slug>/
│       ├── profile.md
│       └── communications/
├── meetings/          # Virtual meeting archives
│   └── YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>.md
├── reports/           # Generated reports
│   ├── weekly/
│   ├── clients/
│   └── technical/
└── README.md          # This file
```

## Usage

- **Client Onboarding:** Use `/office-client-onboard` workflow
- **Project Status:** Use `/office-project-status` workflow
- **Agent Meetings:** Use `/office-agent-meeting` workflow
- **Reports:** Use `/office-report` workflow

## Configuration

Agency configuration is in `.agents/office-config.md`

